<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"/>
    <meta name="screen-orientation" content="portrait">
    <title>拍我自拍节-活动报名</title>
    <style>
        body,div,ul,li,dl,dt,dd,input,button,form,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,img,a,p,span,i,em,strong,address,section,nav,header,footer { 
          margin: 0; 
          padding: 0;
          -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);
        }
        input[type="button"], input[type="submit"], input[type="reset"] { -webkit-appearance: none;}
        li { list-style:none;}
        img { 
          border: none; 
          vertical-align: top;
        }
        em,i,b,address,strong { 
          font-style: normal; 
          font-weight: normal;
        }
        input,textarea,button { 
          border: none; 
          background: none; 
          resize: none; 
          outline: none;
        }

        a { 
          text-decoration: none; 
          color: #b6b3aa;
          font: 14px "helvetica neue","Arial","sans-serif","MicrosoftYaHei","微软雅黑","宋体";}
        body { 
          width: 100%; 
          font: 14px "helvetica neue","Arial","sans-serif","MicrosoftYaHei","微软雅黑","宋体"; 
          color: #b6b3aa; 
          margin: 0 auto;
          background:#f5f5f5;
        }
        html { font-size: 290%;}
        h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6 { 
          font-weight: normal;
        }
        .clear { 
          display: block;
          clear: both;
          content: "";
        }
        
        
       body{
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .main-box{
            width: 7rem;
            height: 10rem;
            
        }
        .avatar{
            width: 2.37rem;
            height: 2.37rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
           
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-top: 1.4rem;
        }
        .avatar img{
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
             border-radius: 50%; 
        }
        
        .nick{
            width: 4.5rem;
            height: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.3rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-size: 0.47rem;
            color: #8a8880;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow:ellipsis;
            white-space:nowrap;
            
        }
        
        .join-ok,.luck_line{
            width: 5.13rem;
            height: 1rem;
            line-height: 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .join-ok img{
            width: 0.78rem;
            height: 0.78rem;
            float: left;
            margin: 0.1rem 0 0 0.314rem;
        }
        
        .join-ok .join_state{
            display: block;
            float: left;
            font-size: 0.686rem;
            color: #414141;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1rem;
            margin-left: 0.47rem;
        }
        
        .luck_line{
            width: 4.82rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .luck_line .line{
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 0.02rem;
            background-color: #8a8880;
        }
        
        .luck_line .line_word{
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -0.745rem;
            width: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #8a8880;
            font-size: 0.353rem;
        }
        
        
        .luck_code{
            width: 4.745rem;
            height: 1.4rem;
            line-height: 1.4rem;
            text-align: center;
            border: 0.078rem solid #ff4c6a;
            border-radius: 0.176rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            color: #ff4c6a;
            
        }
        
        .luck_explain{
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: #8a8880;
            font-size: 0.33rem;
            width: 7rem;
/*
            margin-top: 0.686rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.784rem;
*/
            margin: 0.686rem auto 0.784rem auto;
        }
        
        .luck_explain p{
            line-height: 0.47rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .luck_explain .tm_logo{
            position: relative;
            left: 0px;
            top: -0.118rem;
            font-size: 0.118rem;
        }
        
        .luck_explain .time{
            color: #ff4c6a;
/*            font-weight: 200;*/
        }
        
        .luck_explain .focus{
            font-size: 0.4rem;
            display: block;
            margin-top: 0.2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        
        .question{
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            width: 7rem;
            margin-left: -3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size:0.3rem;
        }
     
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="avatar">
        <img src="{{ avatar }}" alt="">
    </div>
    
    <div class="nick">{{ nick_name }}</div>
    <div class="join-ok">
        <img src="/static/images/join_ok.png" alt="">
        <span class="join_state">报名成功！</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="luck_line">
        <i class="line"></i>
        <span class="line_word">抽奖码</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="luck_code">{{ lucky_num }}</div>
    
    <div class="luck_explain">
        <p>你已成功报名拍我<i class="tm_logo">TM</i>自拍节的抽奖活动</p>
        <p>抽奖环节将在<span class="time">19:30</span>开始，每30分钟进行一轮</p>
        <p class="focus">敬请关注！</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="question">
        <a href="http://paiwo.co/pocket/115703">什么是“拍我自拍节”？</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>